{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act19side_act19side_sub-1-1","storyGroup":"act19side","storySort":11,"storyDependence":"act19side_level_act19side_05_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"DV-S-1","storyName":"困心","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"斐尔迪南为多萝西取来了洛肯水箱实验中回收的数据，可她需要这些数据的理由，却出乎斐尔迪南的意料。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act19side/level/act19side_sub-1-1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act19side_s01","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":9,"next":11,"characters":["斐尔迪南","多萝西"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"Dialog","id":3},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g5_laboratory","screenadapt":"showall","id":4},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"$drift_loop","volume":"0.5","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":10},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"这是你想要的数据。","id":11,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":12},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"谢谢你，斐尔迪南。没想到你会亲自来找我。","id":13,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#2$1","id":14},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"多亏了你与政府部门斡旋，我们回收了洛肯水箱的大部分数据。这一点没必要让太多人知道。","id":15,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":16},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"而且......我想了解下你需要这部分数据的原因。","id":17,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":18},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"......","id":19,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":20},{"type":"Character","id":21},{"type":"Text","text":"她静静地看着面前的显示器，无比专注，甚至放轻了呼吸。","id":22},{"type":"Text","text":"屏幕上正在播放一段录像，录像的主角是一个白发女孩。","id":23},{"type":"Text","text":"大部分时间里，女孩都在睡觉、进食，或者蜷缩在空房间里发呆。","id":24},{"type":"Text","text":"偶尔她会被领到实验室里，隔着一米多厚的隔离墙，将另一间实验室里的桌椅捏成废铁。","id":25},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"真是个美丽的孩子。","id":27,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"你的语气让我想起洛肯·威廉姆斯。我以为只有疯子才会把受试者当成“杰作”到处炫耀。","id":29,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我知道，许多人谴责他突破了道德底线。","id":31,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"道德？那是庸人为了躲避风险而给自己套上的枷锁。","id":33,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#2$1","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"科学本就是超脱常识的。以道德为标准去评价一个科学家，对他而言是莫大的侮辱。","id":35,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"威廉姆斯最大的问题在于，他被眼前无穷无尽的未知逼疯了，丧失了一个科学家应有的理性。","id":37,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"你可以看一眼最后那段录像，看看这个你口中的“美丽的孩子”是怎么把实验室变成天灾现场的——","id":38,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":39},{"type":"Character","id":40},{"type":"Text","text":"屏幕上的画面发生了变化。","id":41},{"type":"Text","text":"当时的监控器并未录下任何声音，可此起彼伏的悲鸣依然穿透了屏幕，冲击着数年之后的另一间实验室。","id":42},{"type":"Text","text":"再多坍塌的砖石都掩盖不掉那满地的血色。","id":43},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"......","id":45,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"这个孩子......她最后去哪了？","id":47,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":48},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"与她有关的数据有明显的被篡改的痕迹。很显然，就和洛肯水箱的全部遗产一样，她对某些组织来说还有利用价值。","id":49,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"斐尔迪南，我想找到她。","id":51,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......","id":53,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我假定你并不是为了继续威廉姆斯的实验而去寻找这个受试者。","id":55,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"她太不可控了。莱茵生命无法承受如此巨大的风险。","id":56,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"......她从来不是自愿地走进实验室。我不能提出这么残忍的要求。","id":58,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"难道你是想治愈她？","id":60,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我们都不是医生，但只要是看过了整个实验过程的人，就不该再抱着这样的妄想。","id":62,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":63},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"不，斐尔迪南。","id":64,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我只是想找到她，然后......抱抱她。","id":66,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"抱......抱她？","id":68,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"这个孩子......她太孤独了。","id":70,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"他们夺去了她的家人，又将她变得与所有人都不一样。","id":71,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1","id":72},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我忍不住想......她现在在哪里？","id":73,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"她有没有认识新朋友，会不会遇上新的敌人？","id":75,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我好想听听她的声音......","id":76,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我改变不了她的过去，但我希望她至少还能拥有未来。","id":78,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"多萝西，你知道吗？你时常让我感到......捉摸不透。","id":80,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"像你这样感情用事的科学家很少见。理性同样无法约束你，说不定哪一天，你会变得比威廉姆斯更加疯狂。","id":81,"figure":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1","id":82},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"......疯狂吗？我曾无数次在梦中见过类似的情形。","id":83,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1","id":84},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"这也是我很想找到这个孩子的原因。","id":85,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"要是她还活着......要是有人能从这么悲惨的过去中拯救她......","id":87,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"那么我相信，假如有一天我当真疯了，也一定会有人来阻止我。","id":88,"figure":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":89},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":90},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":91},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":92},{"type":"Character","id":93},{"type":"Image","id":94}],"characters":["斐尔迪南","多萝西"]}